Modern Times (working title) is a satirical, text-based online multiplayer adventure and role-playing game set in modern-day London. 

It is also an exercise in collaborative game-design. In fact, everybody is invited to contribute! 

Please stay tuned for the release of the first minimalistic public developer preview to get a glimpse of the game's look and feel, and to learn more about the various ways in which you can add your very own texts, ideas, graphics, and game elements to the game.